    "Name": "Sun Bear",
    "Details": "This Special Variant of the Solar Bear, called the Sun Bear, carries 9 Heavy Flamers. Supplied by 6 Tons of Ammunition, Active Probe and Guardian ECM, this Mech is a Danger in Close Quarters. 16 Double Heatsinks, a Heatbank and a Thermal Exchanger try to make it as Cool as possible, but It didnt earn its Nickname by chance.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
